@startuml training_phases
left to right direction
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

rectangle "Grounded warmup" as Warmup
rectangle "Self-play ramp" as Ramp
rectangle "Continuous improvement" as Improve
rectangle "Safety fallback\nif quality drops" as Fallback

Warmup --> Ramp
Ramp --> Improve
Ramp --> Fallback
Fallback --> Warmup
Improve --> Ramp
@enduml
